      "content": "okay i get that. but honestly it's not even like a crisis, it's just this constant heavy feeling in my chest when i move around. it feels more like just being out of shape or catching my breath because i'm older... i don't think it's a real emergency. if i just take a bit more of my usual meds and maybe some extra steam inhalation stuff, it should settle down by tomorrow right? i really just want to avoid the hospital trip if i can.",
